{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CSSOM","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 对象模型</strong> <strong>(CSSOM)</strong> 是树形形式的所有 CSS 选择器和每个选择器的相关属性的映射，具有树的根节点，同级，后代，子级和其他关系。CSSOM 与 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/DOM\">文档对象模型 (DOM)</a> 非常相似。两者都是<strong>关键渲染路径</strong>的一部分，也是正确渲染一个网站必须采取的一系列步骤。</p>\n<p>CSSOM 与 DOM 一起构建<strong>渲染树</strong>，浏览器依次使用渲染树来布局和绘制网页。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cssom_api","title":"CSSOM API","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS 对象模型</a>也是一组 API，允许从 JavaScript 操纵 CSS。它非常类似于 DOM，但应用于 CSS 而不是 HTML。它允许用户动态读取和修改 CSS 样式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"查看更多","title":"查看更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Performance/How_browsers_work\">填充页面：浏览器如何工作</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"查看更多","id":"查看更多"}],"summary":"CSS 对象模型 (CSSOM) 是树形形式的所有 CSS 选择器和每个选择器的相关属性的映射，具有树的根节点，同级，后代，子级和其他关系。CSSOM 与 文档对象模型 (DOM) 非常相似。两者都是关键渲染路径的一部分，也是正确渲染一个网站必须采取的一系列步骤。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Modelo de Objeto CSS (CSSOM)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS 物件模型 (CSSOM)","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/cssom","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/cssom/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CSSOM"